title: S1 E58: Six Minutes of Awards
description:
Holiday  gets  a  scary  glimpse  at  what  her  life  could  have  been  at  WhittierCorp.  The  announcement  of  the  science  competition  winner  makes  life  a  lot  more  complicated  for  the  Anders  family.
